desc.en: Wenzhou Rail Transit is an urban rail transit system serving Wenzhou City and the Wenzhou metropolitan area in Zhejiang Province, China. Its first line opened for trial operation on January 23, 2019. As of August 2023, Wenzhou Rail Transit has opened two lines, namely Wenzhou Rail Transit S1 Line and Wenzhou Rail Transit S2 Line.
